                <div id="6" class="accordion-body collapse" style="height: 0px;">
                    <div class="accordion-inner">
                        <!-- Para -->
                        <p>Absolutely! We use Secure Socket Layer (SSL) encryption to ensure that your personal information cannot be intercepted and read by a third party. Your personal information and your credit card information are converted into bits of code that are transmitted securely. None of our customers have ever reported fraudulent use of their credit card information as a result of giving it to us over the Web, but if you ever suspect that your credit card information is being used without your knowledge, you should contact your credit card company immediately.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>                   
        <h3>Shipping</h3>
            <div class="accordion-group">
                <div class="accordion-heading">
                    <a class="accordion-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#7">
                        <!-- Title. Don't forget the <i> tag. -->
                        <h5><i class="fa fa-plus-square"></i> Shipping Options</h5>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div id="7" class="accordion-body collapse" style="height: 0px;">
                    <div class="accordion-inner">
                        <!-- Para -->
                        <p>We currently offer two shipping options within the contiguous United States. You may choose Standard Ground or Expedited Service. If you choose FedEx Ground most of our customers in the contiguous U.S. receive their orders in just 4 to 5 business days. Need it faster? Expedited will deliver your order within 3 business days after we have filled your order. These shipping times apply to "In Stock" only items.  Items may have delayed shipping estimates.  Delayed shipping estimates are listed for individual items and estimate the time before an item ships.  After an item is shipped it will follow the Standard or Expedited shipping time frames.  Please note that Expedited shipping may not be available on all items.  If you select Expedited shipping we will contact you and inform you if it is available on that item.  We are sorry, but we do not offer Saturday or Sunday delivery. For complete shipping information, visit our Shipping Rate Chart.  For FedEx shipping information visit www.FedEx.com.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>                   
            <div class="accordion-group">
                <div class="accordion-heading">
                    <a class="accordion-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#8">
