                    </a>
                </div>
                <div id="8" class="accordion-body collapse" style="height: 0px;">
                    <div class="accordion-inner">
                        <!-- Para -->
                        <p>We are sorry, but at this time we do not offer any shipping options to countries other than the United States.  Please do not contact us to request shipping to other countries.  We will not ship international under any circumstances.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>                   
            <div class="accordion-group">
