                        <p>
                        If your order appears late, remember:
                        <ul>
                            <li>Credit card approval must be received prior to processing.</li>
                            <li>Expedited orders placed after 12 noon EST are processed the following day.</li>
                            <li>Expedited delivery only occurs on business days (Mondays through Fridays, excluding holidays).</li>
                        </ul>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>                   
            <div class="accordion-group">
