                        <ul>
                            <li>The first confirms that your order has been received (your order confirmation number will be included); this e-mail should arrive within approximately 24 hours.</li>
                            <li>The second confirms that your order has been shipped (any tracking information will be included); this e-mail should arrive within approximately 24 hours after your package is shipped.</li>  
                        </ul>
                        </p>
